Phillip Buchanon was a first-round draft pick for the Oakland Raiders in 2002 . 
  He said his mother demanded he pay her one million dollars as the cost for 'raising him for the last 18 years' after he was drafted into the NFL . 
  Buchanon said he bought his mother a house instead but she lost it . 
  He also said his relatives also asked him for money . 
  He discussed the incident in his book New Money: Stay Rich . 
 